# ============================================================
#  ComfyUI custom nodes — one git URL per line.
#  Lines starting with # are comments and are ignored.
#  To ADD a node:    paste its GitHub URL on a new line.
#  To REMOVE a node: delete its line (or put # in front).
#  After editing: commit -> push -> rebuild.
# ============================================================

